            <title>[KAFKA-6891] send.buffer.bytes should be allowed to set -1 in KafkaConnect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6891</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
